snippet.title: Parappa the Rapper - All Stages [PSP]
snippet.description:
Todos los stages de Parappa the Rapper para PSP en un sólo video, disfrutenlo!

22:52 Full Tank
25:47 Rap Battle

29:21 I gotta believe (Switch subtitles on :) )
31:44 MC King Kong Mushi stage
35:37 Final movie / credits
